description:
This week we go Inside Unqualified again as Anna and Sim sit down to interview a prospective intern named Nina! Both Anna and Sim ask the hard-hitting questions about life, failures, and what it REALLY takes to be an intern at Unqualified. What will happen when she shows up to the interview and Sim tells her Anna’s in a bad mood? Can she handle the pressure? Will she crack when Chris Pratt walks in? This 19-year-old doesn’t know what’s coming so sit in on the interview and see if she gets the job.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
